tring">'<span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123; theme.valine.pageSize &#125;&#125;</span>'</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="number">10</span><span class="string">,</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">visitor:</span> <span class="string">&#123;&#123;</span> <span class="string">theme.valine.visitor</span> <span class="string">&#125;&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&#125;);</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>[not required]</strong> you can also add white list for security</p></li></ol><p><img src="images/hexo_comment_module3.png" alt="paste AppID and AppKey into your theme config file"></p>]]></content>
    
